  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to enter a Rage for 1 minute.</p><p>For the duration, you’re subjected to the following effects:</p><ul><li><p>You deal +1 damage on Melee Attacks.</p></li><li><p>You have ADV on Might Checks and Saves</p></li><li><p>Your PD decreases by 5</p></li><li><p>You gain Resistance (Half) to Elemental and Physical damage.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Ending Early:</strong> Your Rage ends early if you fall Unconscious, die, or you choose to end it for free on your turn.</p>",
